<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wilhelm von Seinsheim zu Hohenkottenheim</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass Jakob Topler, Bürger zu Nürnberg, den Armmann sichert, sofern sein Streit mit Erkinger von Seinsheim wie vorgeschlagen von Wirich IV. von Treuchtlingen vor Michaelstag geschlichtet wird.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_52" id="26r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_52_r1l23">VVılhelm von Sawnſheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l24">ʒu Kottenheım </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_52_line_1576667045063_2296"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> vvılhelm als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt . wıe Jr <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvyrıch<ex>en</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l27"><expan>Treẅtlıng<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>gebett<ex>en</ex></expan> habt ſıch der ſache ʒu <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>winden</expan> <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l28"><expan>Erkıng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von Sawnſheim <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>vett<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>Jacobe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>toppl<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l31">
<add><ab facs="#facs_52_line_1576667113660_2339">doch daʒ dıe ſache </ab><ab facs="#facs_52_line_1576667117050_2344">vor ſand michels </ab><ab facs="#facs_52_line_1576667120956_2349">tag ein end neme </ab></add> Vnd daʒ wır mit <expan>Jacob<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>toppl<ex>er</ex></expan> reden . daʒ er den arm man darauf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_line_1576667090323_2324">ſıcher etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd laſſen euch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l33">daʒ wır mıt <expan>Jacob<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>toppl<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſov<ex>er</ex>r</expan> dauon gerett <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ er vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l34"><expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hat / er welle das alſo aufnemen . doch mıt der = </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_53" id="26v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_53_r1l1">beſchaıden ob ſıch <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vvyrıch von <expan>Treẅtlıng<ex>en</ex></expan> der ſache <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>wınden</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_53_r1l2">vnd vor ſand Mıchelſtag ein end <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan> well als ır das <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_53_r1l4">Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_53_r1l3"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_52" id="26r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wilhelm von Sawnsheim zu Kottenheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Wilhelm, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ir
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Wyrich<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Trewtling<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gebett<ex>en</ex></expan> habt, sich der sache zu
                                <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>winden</expan>
<expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Erking<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von Sawnsheim,
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>vett<ex>er,</ex></expan> und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>Jacobe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Toppl<ex>er</ex></expan>, <add>doch daz die sache vor <app>
<note><q type="date">sand Michels tag</q>29.09.1414</note>
</app> ein end neme</add>, und daz wir mit
                            <expan>Jacob<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Toppl<ex>er</ex></expan> reden, daz er den arm man darauf sicher
                        etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> und lassen euch
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz wir mit
                            <expan>Jacob<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Toppl<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>sov<ex>er</ex>r</expan> davon gerett <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan>
                        daz er uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hat, er welle das also
                        aufnemen, doch mit der <pb facs="#facs_53" id="26v"/>beschaiden, ob sich
                                <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Wyrich von
                            <expan>Trewtling<ex>en</ex></expan> der sache
                            <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>winden</expan> und vor sand Michelstag ein end
                                <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan> well, als ir das
                                <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt. Denn wo wir ewch lieb etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
